{"tid":36920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨人士被台灣統派攻擊 台北市長柯文哲：一定嚴辦！","createTime":"2016-12-13T04:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T07:55:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"162a7d82109b61448ee2ca704387b36e794de9ab","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"港獨人士被台灣統派攻擊 柯P：一定嚴辦！<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-13 12:21<br />\n<br />\n〔記者郭安家／台北報導〕港獨人士、香港民族黨陳浩天、發言人周浩威昨晚於凱薩飯店，與5名愛國心會成員「不期而遇」，並遭愛國同心會成員潑水、丟鞋。外界質疑愛國同心會暴力，台北市長柯文哲今早於市政會議後記者會回應，「不可以在這國家暴力打人，如果這樣話，這國家就等於沒有法律，我們一定會嚴辦！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，本報昨晚報導，警方獲報前往，將兩方人馬都帶回派出所釐清；警方說，由於香港民族黨成員成員要趕搭飛機離台，暫不提告，警方於是先抄取愛國同心會成員的姓名資料，若陳等人事後提告，警方將再依序傳喚涉案人士到案說明。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲今早被媒體詢問此事，柯文哲回應，我們是文明國家，該怎麼就怎麼做，暴力打人就不對，「<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我也會下令警察局該抓的抓，就這樣！該處理的就處理」，不可以在這國家暴力打人，如果這樣話，這國家就等於沒有法律，我們一定會嚴辦！</span><br />\n<br />\n媒體提及，今年七月旅美中國民運人士唐柏橋及異議人士王睿在總統府前受訪，也遭雨傘攻擊，這類事件一而再、再而三發生，是否漠視這類事件？柯文哲說，會下令警察局該怎麼辦、就怎麼辦，我們是文明國家，不允許這種暴力存在。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"c2237e8f809451a8c7d7d00529b28322fd43b269","tid":36920,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f747b2ba92ea7a0569870d58372fad8a65dbfe7","tid":36920,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:45:30.000Z","msg":"愛國同心會成曰係台灣生事宣傳中國，台灣人都會一早搞下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b5aa4d90b6e83412d7f18f0e42cda215a10efa","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92221fc36905889fc0c7fe2833e4c7c0fa81540","tid":36920,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛國同心會成曰係台灣生事宣傳中國，台灣人都唔一早搞下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22e1c83361d39c3e9c56742d6903a557b7bd97dd","tid":36920,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e416ed82270f2d747b6502ff35bb9030cfa5d","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"辱警張秀葉 中國嫁來台<br />\n2015-03-07<br />\n<br />\n〔記者吳張鴻、吳政峰／台北報導〕<span style=\"color: red;\">愛國同心會總幹事張秀葉、成員遇港生，昨日下午因辱罵員警被法辦。據媒體報導，張秀葉是中國配偶，曾自述遭受家暴；遇港生則曾揚言要殺害前總統陳水扁一家人，而被判刑入獄</span>。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的張秀葉，多年前接受公視導演蔡崇隆採訪，錄製「中國新娘在台灣」的紀錄片，自稱1992年嫁來台灣，因家暴而訴請離婚；但前夫反駁，指當年張女登報徵婚，2人多次通信後結婚，婚後張卻不履行同居義務，最後對簿公堂。<br />\n<br />\n遇港生曾揚言要追殺陳水扁一家人，被判刑1年10個月，2年前出獄，又跑到台北市日僑學校噴紅漆，揚言「殺日本人」，被士林地院依恐嚇公眾罪，判處4個月，得易科罰金。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/860693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F860693&d=X6Djyr7Uwvr%2FHWJcRpc4ZEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2c9d93b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F860693&h=76026069\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/860693</a>"},{"pid":"7d6fe2913f7097df31ad6d05b973be1328bfad6e","tid":36920,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柯p"},{"pid":"361cf9377af4183288cab82ac8f34fc266c23116","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柯p</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://images.uncyc.org/zh-tw/thumb/8/8c/柯P高八度大笑.jpg/250px-柯P高八度大笑.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.uncyc.org%2Fzh-tw%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8c%2F%E6%9F%AFP%E9%AB%98%E5%85%AB%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E7%AC%91.jpg%2F250px-%E6%9F%AFP%E9%AB%98%E5%85%AB%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E7%AC%91.jpg&h=69c20cf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8960b8ca4683933beb8ff5765fd42e69d9f5277f","tid":36920,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"係台灣仲安全過係香港呀陰公"},{"pid":"f2405703ec8d9d6df18c0caf2968c9208a85111b","tid":36920,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"拉晒班支那共諜就啱啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412acb0fcece14435ec9ef02d88d0839cb91fea8","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係台灣仲安全過係香港呀陰公</blockquote><br />\n係香港愛國愛黨有公安護航"},{"pid":"b4a7c4aef850b6214b24dd92ead0b4a962fd47f0","tid":36920,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"精人出口 笨人出手<br />\n洗定菊花啦"},{"pid":"187497a475b4528bf27bf97f665c8126a6647a84","tid":36920,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"柯P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc1239870c9e34593f84e1b153c7081bbff40d7","tid":36920,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"柯P市長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54168c5fa86e97c5a6a11bbf7d56c90ca4a268ec","tid":36920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c14d90e4d3318a14978d5043f6756ec5b5e5728","tid":36920,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠：又話勇武？"},{"pid":"4ac8537a093125b65383eda71d74bbde552a8a8a","tid":36920,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"香港政府：不容許違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲以為台灣係一個安全嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同去中國冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}